程序包 com.lss233.phoenix.event.entity

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    AffectEntityEvent
    Triggered when Event is going to be affected.
    DamageEntityEvent
    Represents the base event for when an Entity is being "attacked".
    MoveEntityEvent
    Triggered when a entity moved.
    SpawnEntityEvent
    Triggered when an Event is spawned.
    SpawnEntityEvent.ChunkLoad
    Triggered when an Event is spawned by chunk loading.
    SpawnEntityEvent.Custom
    Triggered when an Event is spawned by custom reason.
    SpawnEntityEvent.Spawner
    Triggered when an Event is spawned by a Spawner.
